Former presidential aide Reno Omokri has argued that a praying wife isn’t always the best. Omokri advised men to rather go for a partner than can pray, slay yet stay as he noted a woman who has these three is the best type of wife.   9ice, wife welcome new child     Adekunle Gold releases much anticipated album     How to know if you’re a side chick/ guy, by Morey Faith   The 48-year-old activist argued a woman can be taught how to pray but beauty is something she either possess or doesn’t. He tweeted: “The best type of wife is not a praying wife, but a wife who can pray, slay and stay. - Advertisement - “Why have 33% when you can get the full 100%? Even if you must get 33%, it is better to choose a woman that can slay. “You can teach prayer. But you either have beauty or you don’t!”